        <main class="space-y-6">
            <!-- Step 1: Initial Assessment -->
            <div id="step1" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg step-card active">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-sky-800">Step 1: Tell Us a Little About Yourself</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">This information helps us personalize your goals. It remains private and is not stored.</p>
                <form id="assessmentForm" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <label for="age" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Age</label>
                        <input type="number" id="age" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500" required>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="gender" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Gender</label>
                        <select id="gender" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500">
                            <option>Female</option>
                            <option>Male</option>
                            <option>Prefer not to say</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                     <div>
                        <label for="weight" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Current Weight (lbs)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="weight" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
                        <div>
                           <label for="heightFt" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Height (ft)</label>
                           <input type="number" id="heightFt" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500" required>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                           <label for="heightIn" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Height (in)</label>
                           <input type="number" id="heightIn" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500" value="0">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-2">
                        <label for="activityLevel" class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">Self-identified Activity Level</label>
                        <select id="activityLevel" class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500">
                            <option value="sedentary">Sedentary (little or no exercise)</option>
                            <option value="lightly_active">Lightly Active (light exercise/sports 1-3 days/week)</option>
                            <option value="moderately_active">Moderately Active (moderate exercise/sports 3-5 days/week)</option>
                            <option value="very_active">Very Active (hard exercise/sports 6-7 days a week)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="md:col-span-2 text-center">
                        <button type="submit" class="w-full md:w-auto bg-sky-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Next: Define Your 'Why' &rarr;</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2: Motivators -->
            <div id="step2" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg step-card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-sky-800">Step 2: What's Your Motivation?</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Understanding your "why" is key to success. Select all that apply.</p>
                <div id="motivators" class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <label class="checkbox-label border-2 border-slate-200 p-4 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-colors flex items-center space-x-3">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="motivator" value="health" class="h-5 w-5 rounded border-slate-300 text-sky-600 focus:ring-sky-500">
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Health</span>
                            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Reduce risk of future health problems.</p>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checkbox-label border-2 border-slate-200 p-4 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-colors flex items-center space-x-3">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="motivator" value="comorbidities" class="h-5 w-5 rounded border-slate-300 text-sky-600 focus:ring-sky-500">
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Co-morbidities</span>
                             <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Better manage existing conditions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checkbox-label border-2 border-slate-200 p-4 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-colors flex items-center space-x-3">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="motivator" value="functional" class="h-5 w-5 rounded border-slate-300 text-sky-600 focus:ring-sky-500">
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Functional Goals</span>
                             <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Improve day-to-day physical abilities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <label class="checkbox-label border-2 border-slate-200 p-4 rounded-lg cursor-pointer transition-colors flex items-center space-x-3">
                        <input type="checkbox" name="motivator" value="appearance" class="h-5 w-5 rounded border-slate-300 text-sky-600 focus:ring-sky-500">
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-semibold text-slate-800">Appearance</span>
                             <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Feel more confident in your skin.</p>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-8 text-center">
                    <button id="calculateBtn" class="w-full md:w-auto bg-sky-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-sky-700 transition-colors shadow-md">See Your Potential &rarr;</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Results & "What If" Scenarios -->
            <div id="results" class="step-card">
                 <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-sky-800">Your Starting Point</h2>
                    <div id="bmiResult" class="text-center bg-sky-50 p-4 rounded-lg"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mt-6">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-sky-800">The "What If" Scenario Projector</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Even small changes can have a big impact. Here's what's possible at different milestones.</p>
                    <div id="scenarios" class="space-y-6"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 3: SMART Goals -->
            <div id="step3" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg step-card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-sky-800">Step 3: Create Your SMART Goal</h2>
                 <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Let's make your goal Specific, Measurable, Achievable, Relevant, and Time-bound. A safe and sustainable rate of weight loss is 1-2 pounds per week.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-4 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                    <p class="flex-grow">I will aim to lose <input type="number" id="weeklyLoss" value="1.5" step="0.5" min="0.5" max="2" class="w-20 text-center rounded-md border-slate-300 shadow-sm focus:border-sky-500 focus:ring-sky-500"> pounds per week.</p>
                    <button id="setGoalBtn" class="bg-emerald-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Set My Goal</button>
                </div>
                <div id="goalTimeline" class="mt-6 text-slate-700 space-y-2"></div>
            </div>

             <!-- Step 4: Education & Next Steps -->
            <div id="step4" class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg step-card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-sky-800">Keep the Momentum Going</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Knowledge is power. Here are some simple tips to support your journey.</p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Benefits of Gradual Loss</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Losing weight slowly (1-2 lbs/week) helps ensure you're losing fat instead of muscle and makes it easier to keep the weight off long-term.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Read Food Labels</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Pay attention to serving sizes, calories, and sugar content. Small adjustments can make a big difference.</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Increase Daily Activity</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Take the stairs, park further away, or go for a short walk during your lunch break. Every little bit helps!</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Prioritize Sleep</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">Lack of sleep can affect hormones that regulate hunger. Aim for 7-9 hours of quality sleep per night.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-6 bg-sky-100 border-l-4 border-sky-500 text-sky-800 p-4 rounded-r-lg">
